-    1. SteelSeries Arctis (user's actual headset mic)
-    2. Realtek built-in mic
-    3. None ÔåÆ sounddevice system default
+    1. preferred_index (if provided and valid)
+    2. SteelSeries Arctis (user's actual headset mic)
